---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Case Study: Mistral Impianti Elettrici - Web Design Roreto | Bitora"
  description="Come abbiamo aiutato Mistral Impianti Elettrici a diventare leader negli impianti elettrici a Roreto con un sito web professionale e lead generation efficace."
>
  <main class="min-h-screen">
    <!-- Hero del progetto -->
    <section class="pt-20 pb-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-cyan-50 dark:from-blue-900/20 dark:to-cyan-900/20">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
          <div class="mb-6">
            <span class="inline-block px-4 py-2 bg-blue-100 dark:bg-blue-800 text-blue-700 dark:text-blue-200 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold mb-4">
              Case Study
            </span>
            <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-6">
              Mistral Impianti Elettrici
            </h1>
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
              Come abbiamo trasformato un'azienda di impianti elettrici di Roreto nel leader locale del settore
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Showcase del progetto -->
          <div class="relative">
            <!-- Logo/Brand Section -->
            <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg mb-6 max-w-md mx-auto">
              <div class="flex items-center justify-center space-x-4">
                <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-600 to-cyan-500 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg">
                  <span class="text-white text-2xl font-bold">⚡</span>
                </div>
                <div class="text-left">
                  <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Mistral</h3>
                  <p class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 font-medium">Impianti Elettrici</p>
                  <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Roreto, TO</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Screenshot mockup -->
            <div class="relative rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-100 to-gray-200 dark:from-gray-700 dark:to-gray-800 p-4">
              <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 rounded-xl shadow-inner overflow-hidden">
                <img 
                  src="/mistral.jpg" 
                  alt="Sito web Mistral Impianti Elettrici - Web Design Roreto"
                  class="w-full h-auto"
                  loading="eager"
                />
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Risultati in evidenza -->
    <section class="py-16 bg-white dark:bg-gray-900">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Risultati Ottenuti</h2>
          
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            <div class="text-center p-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-green-50 to-emerald-50 dark:from-green-900/20 dark:to-emerald-900/20 rounded-2xl">
              <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-green-600 dark:text-green-400 mb-2">+320%</div>
              <div class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200 mb-2">Richieste Preventivi</div>
              <div class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">Incremento nei primi 8 mesi</div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="text-center p-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-cyan-50 dark:from-blue-900/20 dark:to-cyan-900/20 rounded-2xl">
              <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 mb-2">1200+</div>
              <div class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200 mb-2">Lead Qualificati</div>
              <div class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">Generati dal sito web</div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="text-center p-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-50 to-pink-50 dark:from-purple-900/20 dark:to-pink-900/20 rounded-2xl">
              <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-purple-600 dark:text-purple-400 mb-2">180+</div>
              <div class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200 mb-2">Contratti Chiusi</div>
              <div class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">Progetti via canali digitali</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Il problema iniziale -->
    <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
            <div>
              <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">La Sfida Iniziale</h2>
              
              <div class="space-y-6">
                <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
                  <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-red-100 dark:bg-red-900/30 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
                    <span class="text-red-600 dark:text-red-400 font-bold">❌</span>
                  </div>
                  <div>
                    <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Concorrenza Forte Online</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">Grandi catene dominavano le ricerche per "impianti climatizzazione Carmagnola".</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
                  <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-red-100 dark:bg-red-900/30 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
                    <span class="text-red-600 dark:text-red-400 font-bold">❌</span>
                  </div>
                  <div>
                    <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Generazione Lead Inefficace</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">Dipendeva solo dal passaparola e da costose campagne pubblicitarie tradizionali.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
                  <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-red-100 dark:bg-red-900/30 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
                    <span class="text-red-600 dark:text-red-400 font-bold">❌</span>
                  </div>
                  <div>
                    <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Credibilità Digitale Bassa</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">Sito web obsoleto che non trasmetteva professionalità e competenza tecnica.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 text-center text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Situazione Pre-Progetto</h3>
              
              <div class="space-y-4">
                <div class="flex justify-between items-center p-3 bg-red-50 dark:bg-red-900/20 rounded-lg">
                  <span class="font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Posizione Google</span>
                  <span class="text-red-600 dark:text-red-400 font-bold">Pagina 3+</span>
                </div>
                
                <div class="flex justify-between items-center p-3 bg-red-50 dark:bg-red-900/20 rounded-lg">
                  <span class="font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Lead Mensili</span>
                  <span class="text-red-600 dark:text-red-400 font-bold">5-8</span>
                </div>
                
                <div class="flex justify-between items-center p-3 bg-red-50 dark:bg-red-900/20 rounded-lg">
                  <span class="font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Conversione Sito</span>
                  <span class="text-red-600 dark:text-red-400 font-bold">0.8%</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>


    <!-- Timeline del progetto -->
    <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Strategia e Timeline</h2>
          
          <div class="relative">
            <!-- Linea timeline -->
            <div class="absolute left-8 top-0 bottom-0 w-0.5 bg-gradient-to-b from-blue-400 to-purple-600 dark:from-blue-300 dark:to-purple-400"></div>
            
            <div class="space-y-8">
              <!-- Fase 1 -->
              <div class="relative flex items-start space-x-6">
                <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-blue-100 dark:bg-blue-800 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 relative z-10">
                  <span class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-200 font-bold text-lg">1</span>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg flex-1">
                  <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-3">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Analisi Competitiva</h3>
                    <span class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Settimane 1-2</span>
                  </div>
                  <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">Studio del mercato locale, analisi competitor, ricerca keywords tecniche, definizione value proposition.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              
              <!-- Fase 2 -->
              <div class="relative flex items-start space-x-6">
                <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-purple-100 dark:bg-purple-800 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 relative z-10">
                  <span class="text-purple-600 dark:text-purple-200 font-bold text-lg">2</span>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg flex-1">
                  <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-3">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Sviluppo e Contenuti</h3>
                    <span class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Settimane 3-5</span>
                  </div>
                  <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">Creazione sito web tecnico, sviluppo contenuti specialistici, setup lead generation, ottimizzazioni SEO.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              
              <!-- Fase 3 -->
              <div class="relative flex items-start space-x-6">
                <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-green-100 dark:bg-green-800 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 relative z-10">
                  <span class="text-green-600 dark:text-green-200 font-bold text-lg">3</span>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg flex-1">
                  <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-3">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Lancio e Marketing</h3>
                    <span class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Settimane 6-8</span>
                  </div>
                  <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">Lancio campagne Google Ads, attivazione social marketing, monitoraggio performance, ottimizzazioni continue.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Metriche Performance -->
    <section class="py-16 bg-white dark:bg-gray-900">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Performance nel Tempo</h2>
          
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-blue-100 dark:from-blue-900/30 dark:to-blue-800/30 p-6 rounded-xl text-center">
              <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-300 mb-2">Mese 1-2</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-3">Setup e Lancio</div>
              <div class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
                <div>• Sito online</div>
                <div>• SEO base attiva</div>
                <div>• Prime campagne</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-green-50 to-green-100 dark:from-green-900/30 dark:to-green-800/30 p-6 rounded-xl text-center">
              <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-green-600 dark:text-green-300 mb-2">Mese 3-4</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-3">Primi Risultati</div>
              <div class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
                <div>• +150% lead</div>
                <div>• Pagina 1 Google</div>
                <div>• 25 preventivi/mese</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-50 to-purple-100 dark:from-purple-900/30 dark:to-purple-800/30 p-6 rounded-xl text-center">
              <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-purple-600 dark:text-purple-300 mb-2">Mese 5-6</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-3">Crescita Consolidata</div>
              <div class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
                <div>• +250% lead</div>
                <div>• 40 preventivi/mese</div>
                <div>• Crescita costante</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-50 to-orange-100 dark:from-orange-900/30 dark:to-orange-800/30 p-6 rounded-xl text-center">
              <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-orange-600 dark:text-orange-300 mb-2">Mese 7-8</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-3">Obiettivi Superati</div>
              <div class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
                <div>• +320% lead</div>
                <div>• 55+ preventivi/mese</div>
                <div>• Leader di mercato</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Testimonianza cliente -->
    <section class="py-16 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-cyan-600 text-white">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
          <div class="mb-8">
            <span class="text-6xl opacity-30">"</span>
          </div>
          
          <blockquote class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-light mb-8 leading-relaxed">
            Prima faticavamo a trovare clienti, ora dobbiamo gestire un flusso costante di richieste. 
            Il nostro business è completamente cambiato in meglio.
          </blockquote>
          
          <div class="flex items-center justify-center space-x-4">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-blue-600 font-bold text-xl">M</span>
            </div>
            <div class="text-left">
              <div class="font-semibold text-lg">Roberto</div>
              <div class="opacity-90">Titolare, Mistral Impianti Elettrici</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>


    <!-- CTA finale -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-purple-600 text-white">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
          <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">
            La tua azienda può ottenere risultati simili
          </h2>
          
          <p class="text-xl mb-8 opacity-95 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
            Se hai un'attività a Roreto o in Piemonte, possiamo aiutarti a dominare il mercato locale. 
            Scopri come con una consulenza gratuita.
          </p>
          
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-6 justify-center items-center">
            <a href="/contattaci" class="px-8 py-4 bg-primary text-white rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-primary-600 transition-colors text-lg">
              Consulenza Gratuita
            </a>
            
            <a href="/prezzi" class="px-8 py-4 border-2 border-white/60 text-white rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-white/10 hover:border-white transition-colors text-lg">
              Vedi le Soluzioni
            </a>
          </div>
          
          <div class="mt-8 text-sm opacity-80">
            💼 Specialisti B2B • 🎯 Risultati misurabili • 🚀 Crescita garantita
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
